{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_33","type":"agent_message","text":"### Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated library-support job failed to complete `com.querydsl:querydsl-apt:5.0.0` automatically. Preserved work is available here: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2811-library-new-request-com.querydsl-querydsl-apt-5.0.0-8776dd8d\n\nThe most likely failing stage was the generated-test/native verification handoff, not coverage discovery. The generator ran 3 iterations and reached `4/4` dynamic-access coverage (`stats/com.querydsl/querydsl-apt/5.0.0/execution-metrics.json`), and the three generation passes are recorded in `human-intervention-logs/com.querydsl:querydsl-apt:5.0.0/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-12T07-25-00-032552Z.log`, `.../pi-generation-2026-05-12T07-29-07-698808Z.log`, and `.../pi-generation-2026-05-12T07-33-31-742554Z.log`. However, the immediate validation runs still failed under `nativeTest`: `human-intervention-logs/com.querydsl:querydsl-apt:5.0.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-12T07-25-00-045086Z.log` shows `DefaultConfigurationTest` failing with `ClassNotFoundException: com.querydsl.codegen.DefaultVariableNameFunction`, and `.../gradle-test-2026-05-12T07-29-07-736288Z.log` plus `.../gradle-test-2026-05-12T07-33-31-757398Z.log` add `SimpleTypeVisitorAdapterTest` / `HibernateConfigurationTest` failures (`ExceptionInInitializerError` / `NullPointerException`). There is also an environment-specific trace failure in `human-intervention-logs/com.querydsl:querydsl-apt:5.0.0/native-test-verify/cycle-0-generateMetadata-2026-05-12T07-35-36-501301Z.log` reporting `Could not find agent library native-image-agent`.\n\nThe preserved branch contains the likely manual recovery: three library-specific tests plus `NativeCompilerSupport`, native-image runtime args in `tests/src/com.querydsl/querydsl-apt/5.0.0/build.gradle`, and additional metadata in `metadata/com.querydsl/querydsl-apt/5.0.0/reachability-metadata.json`. After those changes, `human-intervention-logs/com.querydsl:querydsl-apt:5.0.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-12T07-54-53-348905Z.log` shows all 3 tests passing and `BUILD SUCCESSFUL`.\n\n1. Check out the preserved branch and review `tests/src/com.querydsl/querydsl-apt/5.0.0/build.gradle`, `tests/src/com.querydsl/querydsl-apt/5.0.0/src/test/java/com_querydsl/querydsl_apt/NativeCompilerSupport.java`, and `metadata/com.querydsl/querydsl-apt/5.0.0/reachability-metadata.json`.\n2. Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=com.querydsl:querydsl-apt:5.0.0` in a GraalVM setup where `native-image-agent` is available, and compare against `human-intervention-logs/com.querydsl:querydsl-apt:5.0.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-12T07-54-53-348905Z.log`.\n3. If validation stays green, use the preserved branch as the basis for the manual PR/update."}}
